{"tid":2267443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李宇軒妹首露面撐12港青  與海外人士拍片 促向中共施壓","createTime":"2020-11-02T05:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T05:45:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd34cb1a49900c804ac7df48b2f415c088c9f547","tid":2267443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/JJM3AQAOZBET5PLDYQWM54T2KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FJJM3AQAOZBET5PLDYQWM54T2KU%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=91f99cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FJJM3AQAOZBET5PLDYQWM54T2KU%2F&h=3e8c8a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/JJM3AQAOZBET5PLDYQWM54T2KU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒妹首露面撐12港青 <br />\n與海外人士拍片 促向中共施壓<br />\n<br />\n【港人送中】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港人至今在深圳鹽田看守所扣押第72日，仍然音訊全無，一班關注12港人安危人士日前發佈短片聲援。其中「香港故事」成員李宇軒的妹妹首度公開露面，與多名海外政界人士一同拍片，呼籲國際社會和各地政府站在公義一方，關注被關押的12港人，並迫使中國對侵犯人權行為負責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gznSxMfe6OecjZy-B4Lki4jSnbI=/1547x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PWTF5XPDPVAZRPGP5XSRSDZC5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgznSxMfe6OecjZy-B4Lki4jSnbI%3D%2F1547x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPWTF5XPDPVAZRPGP5XSRSDZC5I.jpg&h=ca36f884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李宇軒妹妹Beatrice首公開露面，與多名流亡港人及海外人士拍片撐12港人。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n促請各界關注12港人的片段長約兩分鐘，由多位人士用英文作出呼籲，李宇軒的妹妹Beatrice在片中指，被關押12人當中有人患有嚴重抑鬱、哮喘及皮膚病，但家屬不能把相關藥物交到被扣留者手上。12人離開家園後至今音訊全無，家人十分擔心其安危，「因為中共過往一直殘害人權分子及嘗試將他們滅聲」。拍片聲援的港人包括前學民成員許穎婷、協助12港人家屬的本土派人士鄒家成、已流亡的本土民主前線黃台仰和前「民間外交網絡」發言人張崑陽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0NXFzckH3laMEXFNIBYdbs0R31Q=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MIRH6XIWB5AHBDMLUKICLCWXCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0NXFzckH3laMEXFNIBYdbs0R31Q%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMIRH6XIWB5AHBDMLUKICLCWXCM.jpg&h=c3e1fd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李宇軒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E54GcFiYPBBzKkl99ckC_sVIIV0=/785x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LOH7S7OQPFALVKB3XEJ43PM42E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE54GcFiYPBBzKkl99ckC_sVIIV0%3D%2F785x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLOH7S7OQPFALVKB3XEJ43PM42E.jpg&h=a680b4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■影片最後列出12港人的名字，他們至今被扣深圳第72日，音訊全無。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥中共殘害人權分子<br />\n<br />\n在短片發聲的還有人權組織Arise Foundation總監裴倫德（Luke de Pulford）、。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其中Patrizia de Grazia 警告今天「被送中」事件，明天隨時能發生在其他港人身上，國際社會應站在公義一方。裴倫德表示，港府已成為北京的傀儡，甚至把中國的政治議程凌駕於市民的安全。他們共同呼籲國際社會應就事件向中國施壓。他們在影片尾聲手持「#SAVE12HKYOUTHS」標語，一起高呼「Save the 12 Hong Kong Youths, and bring them home（拯救 12 港人，並帶他們回家）」。<br />\n<br />\n許穎婷在fb專頁帖文指，12港人已被關押逾70天，至今仍未能見律師或服藥，國際社會不能承受第13位受害者出現，並代表家屬列明七大訴求，包括立即停即秘密關押，讓家屬委託的律師接觸被告人。"},{"pid":"361013937501e4ff6e21fe9be504909c5680b0ce","tid":2267443,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae07c2008bcfd8d081c25f3b680b88c6746f5e8","tid":2267443,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kqtFMHPjIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9kqtFMHPjIs&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=536ed4fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kqtFMHPjIs</a>"},{"pid":"6c602958e6205129ac532f9492ff392a86a5f73e","tid":2267443,"uid":128287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"施壓?我睇唔到有咩壓力比到中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5ae07c2008bcfd8d081c25f3b680b88c6746f5e8","tid":2267443,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kqtFMHPjIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9kqtFMHPjIs&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=536ed4fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kqtFMHPjIs</a>"}}